Class AplIndexedReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.bigbio.pgatk.io.apl.AplIndexedReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MzIterableReader, MzReader, Serializable, Iterator<Spectrum>

    public class AplIndexedReader
extends Object
implements MzReader, MzIterableReader
    This class implement the JmzReader Interface to provide the information of apl spectra.

        public List<IndexElement> getIndex()
        Returns the index of ms2 queries in the APL file. This ArrayList contains the offsets of all "BEGIN IONS" lines until the end of the "END IONS" lines in the file in the order they are present.
